    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior maintains a solid presence, though a close look will reveal some minor stone chips on the front hood and light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it remains very reliable, offering a smooth driving experience for its next owner.",
