    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant investment to become roadworthy again. The engine currently suffers from major mechanical failures and does not run reliably, while the transmission shows signs of slipping. Externally, the body has several large dents, noticeable rust spots on the wheel arches, and the clear coat is peeling extensively on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears in the fabric, and several electronic components, including the radio and power windows, are non-functional. This is strictly a project car or a parts donor, sold as-is with no warranties implied.",
